item.description:
How about getting out for a walk thru the woods and tossing some discs. You don't have to be good, just throw. Every shot gets closer to the basket ! Here's your chance to walk off some of the thanksgiving turkey. We will meet at Hillside store to gather and get discs. I will hand out some of mine. They also have a great sandwich bar for after if anyone wants to stay and eat. We will then head over to the park and play.

Please remember to wear good shoes and bring water. It is a hike in a way

.Dogs are welcome as long as they don't chase the discs.

This is a FREE event !

Here is some info on the course...http://www.dgcoursereview.com/course.php?id=4935

My number 603-315-0275

** Please only rsvp yes if you are coming. Don't send a no if your not. Thanks**

Cindy
